15 SECTION 7. Arkansas Code § 15-5-901(a)(3), concerning the
16 establishment and uses of the Construction Assistance Revolving Loan Fund, is
17 amended to read as follows:
18 (3) The commission may deposit loans made to and bonds, notes,
19 and other evidences of indebtedness issued by local governmental entities and
20 other owners of environmental projects in accordance with the Clean Water
21 Act, 33 U.S.C. § 1251 et seq., as existing on January 1, 2025, to finance or
